<section id="home" class="active">
<h2>About the University of Jordan</h2>
<p>The University of Jordan is the largest and oldest university in Jordan, founded in 1962. It is located in Amman and offers a wide range of programs in various fields.</p>

<h3>Main Campuses:</h3>
<ul>
<li><a onclick="showSection('engineering')">Faculty of Engineering</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showSection('science')">Faculty of Science</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showSection('library')">University Library</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showSection('sports')">Sports Complex</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showSection('student_center')">Student Center</a></li>
</ul>

