<section id="engineering">
<h2>Faculty of Engineering</h2>
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/01/UJ_Engineering_Building.jpg" alt="Engineering Faculty">
<p>The Faculty of Engineering offers programs in Civil, Mechanical, Electrical, and Computer Engineering. It is equipped with modern labs and workshops.</p>
<h3>Departments:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Civil Engineering</li>
<li>Mechanical Engineering</li>
<li>Electrical Engineering</li>
<li>Computer Engineering</li>
<li>Architecture</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section id="science">
<h2>Faculty of Science</h2>
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/30/UJ_Science_Building.jpg" alt="Science Faculty">
<p>The Faculty of Science provides education in Physics, Chemistry, Biology, Mathematics, and Geology. It has advanced research laboratories.</p>
<h3>Departments:</h3>
<ol>
<li>Physics</li>
<li>Chemistry</li>
<li>Biology</li>
<li>Mathematics</li>
<li>Geology</li>
</ol>
</section>

<section id="library">
<h2>University Library</h2>
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2a/UJ_Library.jpg" alt="Library">
<p>The University Library is the main resource center providing books, journals, and digital resources for students and faculty members.</p>
<ul>
<li>Open daily from 8:00 AM to 10:00 PM</li>
<li>Offers online databases and e-books</li>
<li>Study rooms available for groups</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section id="sports">
<h2>Sports Complex</h2>
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/61/UJ_Sports_Complex.jpg" alt="Sports Complex">
<p>The Sports Complex offers facilities for basketball, football, swimming, and fitness. Students can join various sports clubs.</p>
<ol>
<li>Indoor and Outdoor Courts</li>
<li>Swimming Pool</li>
<li>Gym & Fitness Center</li>
<li>Sports Clubs</li>
</ol>
</section>

<section id="student_center">
<h2>Student Center</h2>
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/53/UJ_Student_Center.jpg" alt="Student Center">
<p>The Student Center is a hub for student activities, events, and cultural programs. It includes cafeterias, meeting rooms, and lounges.</p>
<ul>
<li>Clubs and Societies</li>
<li>Workshops and Events</li>
<li>Cafeterias and Lounges</li>
</ul>
